## 3. Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Frontend Framework** | React Router v7 (Remix) | SSR-capable routing, loaders, TypeScript |
| **Frontend Language** | TypeScript | Type safety across all components |
| **Styling** | Vanilla CSS (custom design system) | Dark theme, glassmorphism, micro-animations |
| **Face Detection** | MediaPipe Tasks Vision (`@mediapipe/tasks-vision`) | Real-time face landmark detection in browser |
| **Backend Framework** | Express.js | REST API, auth orchestration |
| **Backend Language** | TypeScript (compiled via `ts-node` / `tsc`) | Type safety, interfaces shared with DB models |
| **ODM** | Mongoose | MongoDB schema validation and queries |
| **Auth** | JSON Web Tokens (`jsonwebtoken`) | Stateless session management |
| **Password Hashing** | bcryptjs (12 rounds) | Secure credential storage |
| **Email** | Nodemailer (SMTP) | OTP delivery |
| **ML Framework** | FastAPI + Uvicorn | High-performance Python ML serving |
| **Face Embeddings** | DeepFace + ArcFace backend | 512-dim facial feature vectors |
| **Anti-Spoofing** | MiniFASNet (Silent-Face-Anti-Spoofing) | 2D photo / screen replay prevention |
| **Vector Database** | Qdrant Cloud | Face embedding storage + cosine similarity search |
| **Primary Database** | MongoDB (local) | User records, pending signups |

